<div class="container">
  <p id="notice"><%= notice %></p>
  <div class="row section-margin section">
    <div class="col-sm-8">
      <div class="row">
        <h1 class="home-post-title"><%= @post.title.upcase %></h1>
        <p class="col-sm-3 hdr-p">
          <%= image_tag @post.user.avatar_url, class: "media-object, img-circle" %>
          <span id="user"><%= @post.user.name %></span>
        </p>
        <p class="col-sm-5 date hdr-p">
          on <a class="date" href="#"><%= @post.created_at.to_formatted_s(:long_ordinal) %></a>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="row p-top" id="p-no-margin">
        <p>
          <%= simple_format(@post.body) %>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="lw-links">
        <a href="#"><i class="glyphicon glyphicon-comment"></i><span>Read Comments</span></a>
        <a href="#"><i class="glyphicon glyphicon-cloud-upload"></i><span>Upload</span></a>
        <a href="#" id="blue-a"><i class="glyphicon glyphicon-share" id="blue-share"></i><span>Share this post</span></a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-sm-4">
      <div class="row tp-lt-portrait text-center">
        <%= image_tag @post.user.avatar_url, class: "media-object, img-circle" %>
        <h4><%= @post.user.name %></h4>
      </div>
      <div class="row tp-lt-scl-media text-center">
        <p>Twitter</p>
        <p>Facebook</p>
        <p>Instagram</p>
      </div>
      <div class="row tp-lt-ad">
        <div class="text-center">
          <%= image_tag  "surf-boarding.jpg", class: "media-object" %>
        </div>
        <div class="text-right">
            <a class="date" href="#">About this Ad</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row bm-lt-p .rt-sct-container">
          <h3>SideBar Section Heading</h3>
          <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Aspernatur nemo harum, inventore tempore consequuntur perferendis unde impedit repellat esse nulla magnam pariatur alias assumenda cupiditate a, itaque eum, <a href="#" class="date">chic mistape</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <hr>

  <br>

  <div class="col-xs-12">
    <%= link_to 'New Post', new_post_path %>
  </div>
</div>
